---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<section
  class="relative pt-12 pb-4 py-16 md:py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#F8FAFC] to-white overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- subtle background glow -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#0F2E4D]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- LEFT CONTENT -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-8">
          <h2
            class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-[#0F172A] leading-tights"
          >
            Operational Strength in <br />
            Fuel Distribution Indonesia
          </h2>
        </div>

        <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          BAPP’s operational capability is built upon coordinated fuel
          logistics, disciplined supply management, and strategic storage
          deployment.
        </p>

        <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          With integrated supply systems and Floating Storage Unit (FSU)
          infrastructure in Nusa Tenggara Timur (NTT), the company maintains
          consistent fuel availability across Indonesia’s industrial, marine,
          offshore, and mining sectors.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6 mb-8">
          Strategic positioning across key maritime and industrial corridors
          enhances response speed, strengthens supply continuity, and supports
          long-term client operations.
        </p>

        <Button href="/about-us/" text="Our Services" />
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT SIDE – PREMIUM PANELS -->
      <div class="relative space-y-8">
        <!-- PANEL 1 -->
        <div
          class="group relative bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_30px_80px_rgba(15,23,42,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-2"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute -left-3 top-8 w-2 h-12 bg-[#018FF5] rounded-full"
          >
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#0F172A] mb-4">
            Integrated Fuel Logistics
          </h3>

          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Coordinated routing systems and structured fuel logistics enable
            efficient delivery across diverse operational environments,
            minimizing disruption and ensuring timely fuel supply.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- PANEL 2 -->
        <div
          class="group relative bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_30px_80px_rgba(15,23,42,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-2"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute -left-3 top-8 w-2 h-12 bg-[#018FF5] rounded-full"
          >
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#0F172A] mb-4">
            Strategic Storage Infrastructure
          </h3>

          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Floating storage facilities and positioned fuel assets strengthen
            supply resilience, supporting stable fuel distribution across
            Indonesia’s maritime and industrial corridors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- PANEL 3 -->
        <div
          class="group relative bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_30px_80px_rgba(15,23,42,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-2"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute -left-3 top-8 w-2 h-12 bg-[#018FF5] rounded-full"
          >
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#0F172A] mb-4">
            Safety & Operational Discipline
          </h3>

          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Strict fuel handling procedures, quality control standards, and
            governance oversight ensure secure, compliant, and accountable fuel
            distribution operations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
